# cargo-fuzz build output
/target
/Cargo.lock

# Coverage-guided corpus grown by libFuzzer at runtime. Seeds live under
# corpus/<target>/ and ARE committed (they are small, curated real PDFs);
# everything libFuzzer discovers on top is machine-generated and ignored.
/corpus/*/*
!/corpus/*/.gitkeep
!/corpus/*/seed_*

# Crash / timeout / OOM artifacts. When one is found, minimize it and promote
# it into oxidize-pdf-core/tests/fixtures/fuzz-regressions/ (see README), do not
# commit the raw artifact here.
/artifacts
